mkdir node-mongo-crud
cd node-mongo-crud
npm init -y
npm install express mongoose


code structure:
node-mongo-crud/
├── node_modules/
├── package.json
├── package-lock.json
└── index.js

mongod

node index.js

Postman commands:
Action	      Method	  Endpoint	                              Example Body
Create Item	  POST	    http://localhost:3000/items	            { "name": "Laptop", "description": "High-end", "price": 1200 }
Get All Items	GET	      http://localhost:3000/items	            —
Get One Item	GET	      http://localhost:3000/items/:id       	—
Update Item	  PUT	      http://localhost:3000/items/:id        	{ "name": "Gaming Laptop", "description": "Powerful", "price": 1500 }
Delete Item	  DELETE	  http://localhost:3000/items/:id	        —

Use Postman   or any REST client to test these endpoints.